data.description: Welcome to your tranquil retreat in the heart of Nunn, where this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home awaits to embrace you in comfort and serenity. Nestled on a sprawling 1-acre plot of land, this property offers the perfect blend of modern convenience and rustic charm.As you step through the inviting front door, you're greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere, with the main floor living layout designed for effortless flow and functionality. The spacious living area provides the ideal setting for cozy evenings spent by the fireplace pellet stove, or gatherings with loved ones.The heart of the home, the kitchen, boasts ample counter space and storage, making meal preparation a joy. Adjacent to the kitchen, the dining area provides a picturesque backdrop for enjoying your culinary creations, with large sliding glass door overlooking 1 acre of land.Retreat to the comfort of the primary bedroom, complete with a luxurious walk-in bathroom, offering a peaceful oasis for relaxation and rejuvenation. Two additional bedrooms provide ample space for family members or guests, while the second bathroom ensures convenience and privacy for all.Outside, the expansive grounds beckon you to explore and unwind, with plenty of space for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply enjoying the beauty of nature. Whether you're savoring your morning coffee on the porch or stargazing under the night sky, this property offers endless opportunities for leisure and recreation.Conveniently located in a quiet town, yet just a short drive from amenities and attractions in Fort Collins or Greeley, this home offers the perfect balance of tranquility and convenience. Don't miss your chance to make this idyllic retreat your own.
